flowchart TD
    A1[1. Raw Workspace Files<br/>dataset/*] --> A2[2. Ingestion CLI/Pipeline]
    A2 --> A3[3. Guardrails + Metadata Extraction]
    A3 --> A4[4. ingestion_catalog.json + ingestion_audit.json]

    A4 --> B1[5. Retrieval Indexer]
    B1 --> B2[6. DocumentLoader builds chunks]
    B2 --> B3[7. EmbeddingService generates vectors]
    B3 --> B4[8. Milvus collection: kubeflow_artifacts]

    A4 --> C1[9. Artifact Summary Indexer]
    C1 --> C2[10. LLM summary + tags]
    C2 --> C3[11. Milvus: artifact_summaries]

    C3 --> D1[12. Profile Indexer from Summaries]
    D1 --> D2[13. LLM user profiles + skills]
    D2 --> D3[14. Milvus: user_profiles]

    E1[15. platform_documents/*.docx] --> E2[16. Doc ingestion + chunking]
    E2 --> E3[17. Embeddings]
    E3 --> E4[18. Milvus: platform_docs]

    F1[19. User Query via Webapp] --> F2[20. Next.js /api/chat proxy]
    F2 --> F3[21. FastAPI /chat endpoint]
    F3 --> F4[22. ChatEngine classify + rewrite]
    F4 --> F5[23. Intent-routed retrieval]
    F5 --> C3
    F5 --> D3
    F5 --> E4
    F5 --> G1[24. LLM response generation]
    G1 --> F6[25. Structured response with citations]
    F6 --> F7[26. Rendered in chat panel/UI]
